  "remarks": "MOHAMMAD REZA NAQDI was listed pursuant to paragraph 12 of resolution 1737 (2006), as read with resolutions 1747, 1803 and 1929, as: Former Deputy Chief of Armed Forces General Staff for Logistics and Industrial Research/Head of State AntiSmuggling Headquarters, engaged in efforts to get round the sanctions imposed by resolutions 1737 (2006) and 1747 (2007). \n\nThe Director Disqualification Sanction was imposed on 09/04/2025.",
